The '''Tahu'ip''' were an ancient subset of [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] culture on the Twi'lek homeworld [[Ryloth/Legends|Ryloth]]. Its writing technique died out around [[460 BBY]]. By [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]], only three scholars could understand it, including [[For'ali]].

